FRIEDA BELCHATOWSKI v. ABRAHAM BELCHATOWSKI 13 So. (2nd) 314

January Term, 1943

May 11, 1943 Division A Leonard C. Bgert, for appellant. Edward L. Lustgarten, for appellee. *7PER CURIAM:

This is an appeal from a final decree of divorce. The questions propounded have been thoroughly considered but the decree appealed from finds ample support in the record and is affirmed.

Affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
